EXERCISE Geometrische Reihe
@code
let x = rand(2,5);
let q = 1/x;
let res = 1/(1-q) - 1 - q;
@text
Bestimme $ \sum_{k=2}^{\infty} \left(\frac{1}{x}\RRight)^k $
- #res
