EXERCISE Grenzwerte
@code 
let a:b:c = rand(3,8);
let u:v = rand(2,4);
let res1 = a;
let res2 = 0;
let res3 = u^v;
@text
Bestimme die folgenden Grenzwerte:
- $ lim_{x \to \infty} (a \cdot x-b)/x=$ #res1
- $ lim_{x \to -\infty} e^(c \cdot x)=$ #res2
- $ lim_{x \to \infty ( (u \cdot x^2+a)/(x^2+x+b) )^v=$ #res3
